enjoyable to watch and listen to.

1676
01:02:43,725 --> 01:02:46,294
So I do feel a bit pressured to do well.

1677
01:02:46,361 --> 01:02:48,697
There will be eight people
sitting and watching you,

1678
01:02:48,764 --> 01:02:51,499
so I know you can feel pressured.

1679
01:02:51,566 --> 01:02:54,670
Jay Park is probably going to be frowning.

1680
01:02:55,170 --> 01:02:58,206
I sometimes look at the other producers
during our shoot,

1681
01:02:58,273 --> 01:03:00,775
and Jay Park's expression is really scary.

1682
01:03:00,842 --> 01:03:04,446
So I told our members
that they need to stay strong

1683
01:03:04,513 --> 01:03:06,314
