1684
01:03:08,216 --> 01:03:10,352
THAT IS WHY HE PREPARED A PHOTO

1685
01:03:13,689 --> 01:03:16,124
IMAGE TRAINING BEGINS

1686
01:03:17,592 --> 01:03:19,861
ADDING ZICO'S FACE AS WELL

1687
01:03:19,928 --> 01:03:22,497
STARTING PRACTICE WITH JAY PARK AND ZICO
I should show them soon

1688
01:03:22,564 --> 01:03:25,166
WE'RE WATCHING
You'll hear me everywhere

1689
01:03:29,371 --> 01:03:30,972
STAY CALM

1690
01:03:31,506 --> 01:03:32,607
Courage building exercise.

1691
01:03:32,674 --> 01:03:34,142
It scared me too.

1692
01:03:34,209 --> 01:03:35,911
I'm sure it would've been a great help.

1693
01:03:36,912 --> 01:03:38,847
If you have any ideas,
feel free to tell us.

1694
01:03:38,914 --> 01:03:42,717
In MILLI's part,
there's the line "Got it?"

1695
01:03:42,784 --> 01:03:44,319
IDEA 1: JOINING MILLI'S "GOT IT?" PART
and I think it would be cute

1696
01:03:44,386 --> 01:03:46,688
