1697
01:03:46,755 --> 01:03:48,023
Everybody?

1698
01:03:48,090 --> 01:03:49,642
IDEA 2: JOINING MILLI
I think it'll be nice for us

1699
01:03:49,709 --> 01:03:51,559
to join MILLI for the last part.

1700
01:03:51,626 --> 01:03:54,362
IDEA 3: SCATTER FOR THE LAST HOOK
We'll all scatter

1701
01:03:54,429 --> 01:03:56,131
