1702
01:03:56,198 --> 01:03:59,801
IDEA 4: DIVIDING OUTFIT CONCEPTS
Two of us, those two, and OSUN.

1703
01:03:59,868 --> 01:04:00,468
That would be nice.

1704
01:04:00,535 --> 01:04:01,837
ACTIVELY SHARING IDEAS
That sounds good.

1705
01:04:02,370 --> 01:04:03,872
They had lots of ideas

1706
01:04:03,939 --> 01:04:05,640
and actively shared them.

1707
01:04:05,707 --> 01:04:08,310
That's exactly what we wanted from them.

1708
01:04:08,910 --> 01:04:11,346
They asked
for our opinions first,

1709
01:04:11,413 --> 01:04:16,418
and we could freely share our ideas,
so it was nice.

1710
01:04:17,319 --> 01:04:19,354
We should gather often

1711
01:04:19,421 --> 01:04:22,257
and practice the parts
that the producers advised us on.

1712
01:04:22,324 --> 01:04:25,794
We'll have to practice a lot.

1713
01:04:32,267 --> 01:04:35,503
TEAM GRAY X LOCO'S PRACTICE BEGINS

1714
01:04:35,570 --> 01:04:37,338
THINKING

1715
01:04:37,405 --> 01:04:39,874
When we're doing
other people's parts,

1716
01:04:39,941 --> 01:04:42,711
we have to decide
what we're going to do on the side.

1717
01:04:43,845 --> 01:04:45,580
You're going to appear later?

1718
01:04:45,647 --> 01:04:47,615
Yeah, I think so.
It think that looks better.

1719
01:04:47,682 --> 01:04:50,018
Because I'm going
to come out later, right?

1720
01:04:50,085 --> 01:04:54,523
You can be in front of me,
and I can find a way out.

1721
01:04:57,793 --> 01:05:02,197
ACTIVELY DISCUSSING THEIR FORMATIONS

1722
01:05:02,264 --> 01:05:04,099
Since it's a team mission,

1723
01:05:04,166 --> 01:05:08,503
there were a lot of formations
and parts we had to discuss.

1724
01:05:08,570 --> 01:05:10,772
So we met up often to practice.

1725
01:05:16,978 --> 01:05:19,114
TEAM GRAY X LOCO
MET EVERY DAY TO PRACTICE

1726
01:05:19,181 --> 01:05:20,148
How do you feel about this?

1727
01:05:20,215 --> 01:05:21,483
Pretty good.

1728
01:05:21,550 --> 01:05:23,418
I bet we would've
practiced the most.

1729
01:05:23,485 --> 01:05:26,621
Good. Very good.

1730
01:05:27,322 --> 01:05:29,724
We're practicing really hard.

1731
01:05:29,791 --> 01:05:33,261
MILLI PRACTICING
HER KOREAN PRONUNCIATION

1732
01:05:33,328 --> 01:05:36,264
I should show them soon

1733
01:05:36,331 --> 01:05:39,734
OXYNOVA HELPS MILLI
I should show them soon

1734
01:05:40,368 --> 01:05:42,904
While preparing for this mission,

1735
01:05:42,971 --> 01:05:44,639
we met pretty often,

1736
01:05:44,706 --> 01:05:47,575
so we started to seem like a family.

1737
01:05:47,642 --> 01:05:52,313
The older members
helped keep the vibe relaxed,

1738
01:05:52,380 --> 01:05:54,382
so we grew close pretty quickly.

1739
01:05:54,449 --> 01:05:56,329
Thank you so much
for taking care of me

1740
01:05:56,396 --> 01:06:00,788
