1744
01:06:16,104 --> 01:06:17,606
Thank you for that.

1745
01:06:19,374 --> 01:06:21,876
This is GRAY's studio.

1746
01:06:21,943 --> 01:06:23,645
He said we could use his studio
whenever we wanted.

1747
01:06:23,712 --> 01:06:25,280
He even got us grills.

1748
01:06:25,347 --> 01:06:28,616
Our producers have been taking care of us

1749
01:06:28,683 --> 01:06:30,485
