1753
01:06:36,758 --> 01:06:37,859
We'll be able to see that on stage.

1754
01:06:37,926 --> 01:06:41,463
That's why we have to support them well.

1755
01:06:43,832 --> 01:06:45,700
TEAM GRAY X LOCO IS PRACTICING
THE NEXT DAY

1756
01:06:45,767 --> 01:06:48,603
LOCO HELPS THEM WITH THE PERFORMANCE

1757
01:06:48,670 --> 01:06:51,005
If it's too intense...

1758
01:06:51,072 --> 01:06:51,673
GRAY AND LOCO ACTIVELY HELP THE MEMBERS

1759
01:06:51,740 --> 01:06:52,941
I think this is better.

1760
01:06:53,008 --> 01:06:54,475
Yeah, much better.

1761
01:06:54,542 --> 01:06:56,945
It sounded nice.

1762
01:06:58,880 --> 01:07:00,849
They came and watched
during our practice.

1763
01:07:00,916 --> 01:07:02,851
They even stayed until we finished.

1764
01:07:05,153 --> 01:07:06,321
Great work.

1765
01:07:08,823 --> 01:07:13,895
TEAM GRAY X LOCO EVEN SPENT
NEW YEAR'S TOGETHER

1766
01:07:13,962 --> 01:07:16,564
3, 2, 1.

1767
01:07:16,631 --> 01:07:19,868
Happy New Year!

1768
01:07:19,935 --> 01:07:21,369
Happy New Year.

1769
01:07:21,436 --> 01:07:25,006
They're so warm and kind.

1770
01:07:25,073 --> 01:07:30,245
We can feel
that they're sincerely caring for us.

1771
01:07:30,312 --> 01:07:33,081
LOCO'S SEOUL CONCERT

1772
01:07:33,148 --> 01:07:36,618
We're here
for LOCO's concert. Congratulations, LOCO.

1773
01:07:36,685 --> 01:07:38,353
Thank you for the invites.

1774
01:07:38,420 --> 01:07:39,061
Thank you.

1775
01:07:39,128 --> 01:07:44,392
