to practice on such a large stage.

1776
01:07:44,492 --> 01:07:45,226
You know what I'm saying?

1777
01:07:45,293 --> 01:07:46,694
It's a "note"-able honor.

1778
01:07:46,761 --> 01:07:48,897
COLD GAZE AT THE DAD JOKE

1779
01:07:48,964 --> 01:07:52,533
I was actually wondering
what I could do for them,

1780
01:07:52,600 --> 01:07:54,702
and I decided to spare
some of my rehearsal time

1781
01:07:54,769 --> 01:07:56,137
to let them gain experience

1782
01:07:56,204 --> 01:07:58,373
