1783
01:08:01,676 --> 01:08:03,878
THEY WERE ABLE TO PRACTICE ON THE STAGE

1784
01:08:03,945 --> 01:08:07,081
Ssak, ssak, sweep up everything

1785
01:08:07,148 --> 01:08:09,684
I should show them soon

1786
01:08:09,751 --> 01:08:13,254
They even memorized
the lyrics for each other's parts

1787
01:08:13,321 --> 01:08:15,857
