1788
01:08:15,924 --> 01:08:17,592
They were pretty cool.

1789
01:08:22,931 --> 01:08:24,766
PROUD

1790
01:08:26,501 --> 01:08:27,635
How was it?

1791
01:08:27,702 --> 01:08:28,403
It was great.

1792
01:08:28,470 --> 01:08:29,938
It's easy money.

1793
01:08:30,805 --> 01:08:31,740
How was it?

1794
01:08:32,707 --> 01:08:34,142
It was good.

1795
01:08:34,209 --> 01:08:36,277
I can imagine us doing a tour together.

1796
01:08:37,212 --> 01:08:38,112
Our producers
are really considerate.

1797
01:08:38,179 --> 01:08:40,782
I could sense how they were trying

1798
01:08:40,849 --> 01:08:42,884
to respect all of us.

1799
01:08:42,951 --> 01:08:45,487
They're really cool guys.

1800
01:08:46,254 --> 01:08:48,723
GRAY IS FILMING

1801
01:08:49,424 --> 01:08:52,460
We met
about eight times a week.

1802
01:08:52,527 --> 01:08:55,864
I met my teammates more often
than my mom this past week.

1803
01:08:56,831 --> 01:09:00,301
We have perfect teamwork
and faith in each other.

1804
01:09:01,903 --> 01:09:04,105
We'll show you
what real teamwork is.

1805
01:09:05,373 --> 01:09:06,474
DAY OF THE MISSION

1806
01:09:06,541 --> 01:09:08,476
GRAY X LOCO'S GENEROUS SUPPORT

1807
01:09:08,543 --> 01:09:09,610
STEAK MEAL DELIVERY

1808
01:09:09,677 --> 01:09:11,179
