2991
01:52:43,989 --> 01:52:45,824
But since everyone did great,

2992
01:52:45,891 --> 01:52:48,527
the performances and songs were amazing.

2993
01:52:48,594 --> 01:52:51,763
Yeah, none of them
were similar.

2994
01:52:51,830 --> 01:52:54,099
Yeah, every song was different.

2995
01:52:54,166 --> 01:52:57,035
It was our first performance as a team.

2996
01:52:57,102 --> 01:53:01,273
So it felt really new to see them
performing on stage

2997
01:53:01,340 --> 01:53:04,843
as a team after all that practice.

2998
01:53:04,910 --> 01:53:08,847
I felt really anxious yet excited
during the performance.

2999
01:53:08,914 --> 01:53:12,150
I had mixed feelings as I watched.

3000
01:53:12,217 --> 01:53:16,788
But I'm grateful everyone
did such a great job.

3001
01:53:16,855 --> 01:53:20,158
We should use today as a chance to refocus

3002
01:53:20,225 --> 01:53:23,729
and prepare even harder
for the next mission.

3003
01:53:23,796 --> 01:53:26,431
We have to keep going forward.
There's a lot to do.

3004
01:53:26,498 --> 01:53:28,567
TO BE CONTINUED SHORTLY
I hope we keep our focus until the end.

3005
01:53:28,634 --> 01:53:31,269
- Let's be the coolest team.
- Yeah.

3006
01:53:31,336 --> 01:53:33,372
The more intense and cruel...

3007
01:53:33,439 --> 01:53:34,840
Team Diss Mission.

3008
01:53:34,907 --> 01:53:36,341
The Diss Mission.
It's finally time.

3009
01:53:36,408 --> 01:53:37,576
I've been waiting for this moment.

3010
01:53:37,643 --> 01:53:39,645
I'm great at making people angry.

3011
01:53:43,315 --> 01:53:44,483
