WITH THE TEAM'S PRIDE ON THE LINE

3012
01:53:44,550 --> 01:53:45,784
What are you saying?

3013
01:53:46,819 --> 01:53:48,286
Are they really on bad terms?

3014
01:53:48,353 --> 01:53:50,322
It's been a while
since things were so hardcore.

3015
01:53:50,389 --> 01:53:52,224
Our team is full of real bullies.

3016
01:53:52,291 --> 01:53:53,792
We're going
to crush those bullies.

3017
01:53:53,859 --> 01:53:55,127
TEAM DISS MISSION
GRAY, LOCO VS LIL MOSHPIT, JAY PARK

3018
01:53:55,194 --> 01:53:56,595
OSUN VS ZENE THE ZILLA'S LEGENDARY STAGE

3019
01:53:56,662 --> 01:53:58,196
SOMETHING EVEN MORE LEGENDARY?
That's brutal.

3020
01:53:59,665 --> 01:54:00,866
I'll make a hit song for you.

3021
01:54:03,268 --> 01:54:05,537
1, 2, 3, 4, OSUN

3022
01:54:05,604 --> 01:54:07,839
No matter how hard you try
You can't be HAON

3023
01:54:10,275 --> 01:54:11,543
TEAM DISS MISSION
ZICO, CRUSH VS J-TONG, HUKKY SHIBASEKI

3024
01:54:11,610 --> 01:54:13,445
NOWIMYOUNG versus HAON.

3025
01:54:13,512 --> 01:54:14,880
Family drama is the best.

3026
01:54:14,947 --> 01:54:16,214
KC family fight.

3027
01:54:16,281 --> 01:54:19,418
I'm KC, you're retired

3028
01:54:19,485 --> 01:54:20,919
Height is 160

3029
01:54:20,986 --> 01:54:21,620
Just a little kid

3030
01:54:21,687 --> 01:54:23,088
Looks like
he got hit pretty hard.

3031
01:54:23,155 --> 01:54:24,222
Leave KC. Let's go!

3032
01:54:24,289 --> 01:54:26,992
Hip-hop is about being cool?
It's all about skill, idiot.

3033
01:54:29,495 --> 01:54:30,362
He looks really angry.

3034
01:54:30,429 --> 01:54:31,596
Are they going to cut ties?

3035
01:54:31,663 --> 01:54:33,031
Are you sure
you're okay with this?
